        <zone friendly-name='hor.findings(insights)' h='93333' hidden-by-user='true' id='126' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='100000' x='0' y='6667'>
          <zone fixed-size='22' h='3333' hidden-by-user='true' id='127' is-fixed='true' type-v2='empty' w='100000' x='0' y='6667'>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='79445' hidden-by-user='true' id='129' type-v2='text' w='100000' x='0' y='10000'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Welcome : </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>&lt;Full Name&gt;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Customer Insights &amp; Recommendations</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Key Findings</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Churn is high (59.78%), with more customers leaving than remaining active, indicating a retention issue.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Average revenue is negative, suggesting refunds or low retention are impacting profitability.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Refund behavior closely aligns with churn, pointing to customer dissatisfaction.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Purchase frequency is the strongest indicator of retention, while inactivity significantly increases churn risk.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>High spend does not guarantee loyalty, meaning valuable customers are still at risk of leaving.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Customer Insights</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>A large portion of customers fall into at-risk segments with low engagement.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>A smaller group of loyal, high-value customers contributes most of the revenue.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>New customers show low engagement and require nurturing to become repeat buyers.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Recommendations</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Prioritize re-engagement of at-risk customers through targeted campaigns.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Investigate and address causes of refunds to improve customer satisfaction.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Strengthen retention of high-value customers with loyalty-focused initiatives.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Increase purchase frequency through promotions and personalized engagement.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Improve onboarding to convert new customers into long-term users.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Conclusion</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Retention is the primary challenge. Focusing on engagement, reducing refunds, and protecting high-value customers will have the greatest impact on improving performance.</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>AUTHOR</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>:  </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>TIMOTHY MAINA</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone fixed-size='22' h='3333' hidden-by-user='true' id='128' is-fixed='true' type-v2='empty' w='100000' x='0' y='89445'>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='background-color' value='#000000db' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
